OL,7,FTwo serving police officers from will
OL,8,Fface gross misconduct hearings for
OL,9,Fsharing offensive WhatsApp messages,
OL,10,Faccording to the police watchdog.
OL,12,FIn 2023, the (IOPC) began
OL,13,Finvestigating several former and
OL,14,Fserving officers at the force after
OL,15,F"derogatory and inappropriate
OL,16,Fmessages" were found on a deceased
OL,17,Fofficer's phone.
OL,19,FRicky Jones' family found the on his
OL,20,Fphone after he died and handed them to
OL,21,Fthe force.
