OL,7,FGwent Police Chief, Pam Kelly, said,
OL,8,F"We have been abundantly clear that we
OL,9,Fwill not tolerate poor behaviour and
OL,10,Fthis case should act as a stark
OL,11,Fwarning".
OL,13,FTwo serving constables and a former
OL,14,Fconstable will now have to answer for
OL,15,Fgross misconduct, for exchanging
OL,16,Fracist, misogynistic and homophobic
OL,17,Fmessages. They will face the hearings
OL,18,Flater this year.
