OL,7,FThe IOPC director, David Ford said,
OL,8,F"The content of some of the messages
OL,9,Fwe examined raised serious concerns
OL,10,Fabout the conduct of those police
OL,11,Fofficers involved.
OL,13,F"We did not find any evidence to
OL,14,Fsubstantiate an allegation that Gwent
OL,15,FPolice tried to cover up inappropriate
OL,16,Fmessages, which might have indicated
OL,17,Fcorruption. The evidence showed that
OL,18,Fthe searches police carried out on
OL,19,FRicky Jones' phone were reasonable and
OL,20,Fproportionate in the circumstances at
OL,21,Fthe time.
